reagent-name-rmcgenerictoxin = Generic Toxin
reagent-desc-rmcgenerictoxin = General identification for many similar toxins, sometimes created as a byproduct through chemical reactions.

reagent-name-rmcmolecularacid = Diluted Molecular Acid
reagent-desc-rmcmolecularacid = An acid of unknown composition, this sample doesn't seem to be as dangerous those found within Xenonid bloodstreams.

rmc-body-stings = Your body stings slightly.

reagent-name-rmclexorin = Lexorin
reagent-desc-rmclexorin = Lexorin is an extremely dangerous compound that damages tissue and paralyzes the lungs, effectively stopping respiration. Can be deadly in even small doses. Lexorin is effectively countered by variants of dexalin.

reagent-name-rmcmindbreakertoxin = Mindbreaker Toxin
reagent-desc-rmcmindbreakertoxin = A powerful hallucinogenic compound that is illegal under Marine Law. Causes extreme hallucinations and is very addictive. Formerly known as LSD.

reagent-name-rmcblackgoo = Black Goo
reagent-desc-rmcblackgoo = A strange substance of unknown origin. . .

reagent-name-rmc-chloral-hydrate = Chloral Hydrate
reagent-desc-rmc-chloral-hydrate = Chloral hydrate was the first synthetically produced sedative-hypnotic drug. It is a powerful sedative which causes near instant sleepiness, but can be deadly in large quantities. Often used together with other anesthetics for surgical procedures.

reagent-name-rmc-xenoalch-brute = Sagunine
reagent-desc-rmc-xenoalch-brute = A xenonid alchemical toxin that causes brute trauma and breaks down brute medicines.

reagent-name-rmc-xenoalch-burn = Cholinine
reagent-desc-rmc-xenoalch-burn = A xenonid alchemical toxin that causes caustic burns and breaks down burn medicines.

reagent-name-rmc-xenoalch-pain = Noctine
reagent-desc-rmc-xenoalch-pain = A xenonid alchemical toxin that increases pain and breaks down painkillers.

reagent-name-rmc-xenoalch-fire = Pyrinine
reagent-desc-rmc-xenoalch-fire = A xenonid alchemical toxin that overheats the victim.

reagent-name-rmc-xenoalch-bloodloss = Vapinine
reagent-desc-rmc-xenoalch-bloodloss = A xenonid alchemical toxin that destroys blood in the victim's bloodstream.

reagent-name-rmc-xenoalch-freeze = Crynine
reagent-desc-rmc-xenoalch-freeze = A xenonid alchemical toxin that chills the victim and breaks down cryogenic medicines.

reagent-name-rmc-xenoalch-purge = Xenosterine
reagent-desc-rmc-xenoalch-purge = A xenonid alchemical toxin that strips non-toxic chemicals from the victim's bloodstream.
